name: Verify Title Is Visible
description:
This test checks whether the JLT homepage title is "Start - Jönköpings Länstrafik".
Steps:
1. Check if Homepage is visible
2. Get the title of the homepage
3. Verify that the title is "Start - Jönköpings Länstrafik".
